desc.en:
Chenjiang City is my overhead city, some of the station names in it are references to real station names. It can be shared to some friends who want to make an overhead city, but please don't use it for commercial purposes, thank you!
The name Chenjiang City is a random name I made up, it has nothing to do with the real Chenjiang Town!!!!
Chenjiang city metro line is now saturated development, the metro company said that the planning task has been completed, the near future (meaning within fifty years) will not plan new lines and construction of new lines, so the map is now complete.
The following is the official announcement of the Chenjiang Metro Company (overhead) line first pass time and grouping:
